description: Keane Mulready-Woods went missing from his County Louth home on Sunday.
title: Drogheda feud: Remains confirmed as those of missing teenager
title_page: Drogheda feud: Remains confirmed as those of missing teenager - BBC News
maintext: The police also believe that human remains found in a burning stolen car at Trinity Lane off Clonliffe Avenue in Ballybough in the early hours of Wednesday morning are those of Keane's, but they are waiting on DNA confirmation.
